834
01:24:39,480 --> 01:24:40,754
<font color="#808080">ELISE:</font>
There.

835
01:24:42,040 --> 01:24:43,678
There.

836
01:24:44,120 --> 01:24:46,236
Behind the medallion. There.

837
01:25:25,760 --> 01:25:26,829
Open it.

838
01:25:31,720 --> 01:25:33,756
