858
01:27:08,640 --> 01:27:09,834
<font color="#D900D9">(IN RUSSIAN)</font>
This was the man on the boat.

859
01:27:10,160 --> 01:27:13,277
- He is not Alexander Pearce.
- <font color="#808080">FRANK:</font> Elise, please.

860
01:27:13,440 --> 01:27:16,398
- What the hell are you doing?
- <font color="#808080">ACHESON:</font> What the hell is he doing?

