894
01:28:54,280 --> 01:28:58,671
Open the safe now, and I won't
make you watch something

895
01:28:58,840 --> 01:29:01,559
that you would never forget.

896
01:29:02,720 --> 01:29:04,392
Open it.

897
01:29:09,440 --> 01:29:10,953
