916
01:31:41,400 --> 01:31:42,435
Thank you, sir.

917
01:31:46,120 --> 01:31:47,280
<font color="#808080">AGENT:</font> <font color="#D900D9">(ON RADIO)</font>
We got him.

918
01:31:47,400 --> 01:31:49,595
- We got Alexander Pearce.
