01:32:46,440 --> 01:32:48,158
<font color="#D900D9">(BEEPING)</font>

929
01:33:01,840 --> 01:33:04,400
<font color="#D900D9">(♪♪♪)</font>

930
01:33:14,680 --> 01:33:16,830
